stie Hayes to leave 'Home and Away'|last=Rowe|first=Darren|date=17 August 2009|publisher=[[Digital Spy]]|accessdate=21 February 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Max Sutherland (Home and Away)|Max Sutherland]] || [[Sebastian Elmaloglou]] || 2002\u20132004 || <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.digitalspy.com/soaps/home-and-away/a783148/you-wont-believe-what-little-max-sutherland-from-home-and-away-looks-like-now/|title=You won't believe what little Max Sutherland from Home and Away looks like now|last=Dainty|first=Sophie|date=11 February 2016|publisher=[[Digital Spy]]|accessdate=21 February 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Rhys Sutherland]]|| [[Michael Beckley]] || 2000\u20132004 || <ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.dailyedge.ie/did-you-recognise-that-guy-on-raw-last-night-781750-Feb2013/|title=Did you recognise that guy on Raw last night?|date=4 February 2013|work=[[Daily Edge]]|accessdate=24 February 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Shelley Sutherland]]|| [[Paula Forrest]] ||  2000\u20132004, 2009 || <ref>{{cite web|url=http://au.tv.yahoo.com/home-and-away/features/article/-/article/6393344/farewell-kirsty|title=Farewell Kirsty|publisher=[[Yahoo!7]]|accessdate=23 December 2011|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100102043339/http://au.tv.yahoo.com/home-and-away/features/article/-/article/6393344/farewell-kirsty/|archivedate=2 January 2010|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==T==\n{| class=\"wikitable\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" width=\"250\" | Character\n! scope=\"col\" width=\"250\" | Actor(s)\n! scope=\"col\" width=\"300\" | Duration\n! scope=\"col\" class=\"unsortable\"| {{Abbr|Ref(s)|Reference(s)}}\n|-\n|  Liam Tanner || Peter Scarf || 1996\u20131997 || <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.digitalspy.com/showbiz/a192978/taylor-dating-ex-home-and-away-star/|title=Taylor dating ex-'Home and Away' star?|last=Davies|first=Rebecc|date=29 December 2009|publisher=[[Digital Spy]]|accessdate=16 February 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|  [[Belle Taylor]]|| [[Jessica Tovey]] || 2006\u20132009 || <ref>{{cite web|url=https: